## Why MIT License?

The MIT License is chosen because:

✅ **Simple and permissive** - Easy to understand
✅ **Developer-friendly** - Allows commercial use
✅ **Popular** - Used by major projects (jQuery, Rails, Node.js, etc.)
✅ **Business-friendly** - Companies feel comfortable using it
✅ **Flexible** - Can be used in open source or proprietary projects

